    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-simulation-lab-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Validation uncertainty (±12%) is acceptable for the intended comparative use of the model. Decision supported by the bound requirement (morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and claim (morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis) documentation.",
